articles.title: Week 6 NFL Power Rankings: And your playoff chances are ...
articles.description: The Jaguars are no longer just fringe contenders. The Eagles are emerging as the NFC favorite. And the undefeated Chiefs are the closest thing to a lock as it comes. Here's a look at all 32 teams' postseason hopes.

articles.title: Best and worst QBs of Week 5: Welcome to the Deshaun and Dak show
articles.description: The top performances belonged to young stars Deshaun Watson and Dak Prescott, who had huge days in losing efforts.
